Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}候麦《六个道德故事》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之一《蒙索的面包店女孩》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.73,0:00:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}巴黎  维立尔路口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.36,0:00:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}东边  巴迪格尔大街
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}北边  勒维斯大街和市场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}维立尔的多姆咖啡馆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在它右边是维立尔大街
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:00:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}维立尔地铁站
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.86,0:01:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}西边是古塞尔大街
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.43,0:01:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直延伸到蒙索公园
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.86,0:01:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和前城市俱乐部的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}学生住宅区
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我还在法律学校的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每晚在那里吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}同时希尔维在蒙索大街上的画廊工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.73,0:01:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}穿过公园回到家里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.86,0:01:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只是见过她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.36,0:01:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们经常在十字路口和俱乐部之间擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.99,0:01:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们偶尔交换眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.59,0:01:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但再无其它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要往后看  她对我来说高了点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}斯密德  我的朋友  总是鼓励我行动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我总是害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.36,0:01:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}试试看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.26,0:01:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么  跟她搭讪？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.03,0:01:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么不  总有机会的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我倒是想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但她绝不是那种可以在街上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被随便搭讪的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且我看起来也不是她喜欢的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.66,0:02:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我认为她准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.86,0:02:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为我偶尔破例一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也准备这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.86,0:02:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但还是太冒失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不想冒险去做我不擅长做的事清
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很久吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比往常要久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.93,0:02:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听着  我想跟着她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要  直接跟她说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直接找她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我能感觉到自己对她强烈的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在是5月  将近学年结束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.69,0:02:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她应该住在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们见过她好几次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拿着篮子买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看见没  小声点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我什么都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.49,0:02:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她也许住在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等会  小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她进了一个商店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她故意不看我们 但做得太明显了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不管  我要跟着她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算我可以让她察觉不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但这样做有什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我等会来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我决定采取行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幸运女神终于降临到我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们没撞上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢天谢地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有次差点撞到脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幸好你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说差点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没受伤  车子太吵了  听不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要补偿你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}过半个小时在咖啡店见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今晚比较忙  下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反正我们经常见面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}经过这次简短的交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只有一个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下次留住她  不管说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.36,0:04:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后洗刷掉这次冒失的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.49,0:04:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很明显 我胜利在望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我得承认突然撞上她并不完全是意外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她看起来也不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}相反  她还有回应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她虽然拒绝了约会 但没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从现在开始  下次再见到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她就可以聊天了  就在不久之后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我期望的终于发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但厄运也随着好运而来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三天过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后是一个星期
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没见到她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}斯密德因为要考试就回到家中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然深陷这段感情中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我从没有过放弃学业
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去找希尔维的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我唯一的空闲时间就是吃饭时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我没有吃晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚餐花了30分钟  我来回走了3回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我能遇上希尔维的机率翻了10倍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但这条街上没有收获
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她也许走了另一条路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她也许坐地铁或者乘公车
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但不管怎样  她都要买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我决定扩大我在勒维斯大街上的搜寻范围
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然而  我得说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这几个下午的街道非常炎热
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无聊又疲劳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}市场上的东西很丰富很新鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}美好的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让我胃口大开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不想去咖啡店  假期快来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}樱桃时节正好给馋嘴的人们提供了好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在埋头看书好几个钟头后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}市场的气味和声音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比俱乐部更能让人放松
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的搜寻再次无功而返
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里的人太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也许是巴黎人口密度最高的地区之一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我该放弃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}该回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我还年轻还愚蠢地希望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能看见她出现在某个窗口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或者从某个商店出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再次和她面对面  像那天一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.03,0:07:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我决定四处走走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我在勒波特大街上发现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个小小的面包店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我曾经经常在那里买曲奇和面包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}作为主食来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等会  杰琪  明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让我工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}女孩子真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.36,0:08:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在说什么  离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是个蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}曲奇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他让我脑火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}带走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}40法郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}曲奇的味道和其它面包房一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它们都是机器生产
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在哪儿都可以找到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一方面  我可以不被希尔维看见我在吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也许在拥挤的市场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她会意外出现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}另一方面  买曲奇吃成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和面包房女孩之间的某种仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在我这个年纪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你最恨的莫过于买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我喜欢走进一个商店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感觉像是第一次进入
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个女孩认出我来 陪我玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好  小姐  一个曲奇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}40法郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是没有见到希尔维
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是在躲我吗  为什么  老天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她去乡下了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生病呢  死呢  结婚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这些都有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到这个星期结束时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的等待不过是形式而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我更想马上冲到面包店
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每次很小心地进门
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的拖拖拉拉和我奇怪的举止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}两个曲奇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}该死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事  分开包
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等会  我好像有零钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很容易看出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个面包店女孩对我有好感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你说我虚荣也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}女孩子喜欢我是很自然的一件事清
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而她又不是我喜欢的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}希尔维
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直占据着我的脑海
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的  因为我一直想着希尔维
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.19,0:12:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才接受了来自面包店女孩的暖昧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感觉好像我没有爱上另一个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的  一个曲奇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个卷筒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让我看看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}罗兰蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还要什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分开包吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是  但不要曲奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}给我一份杏桃塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我每天沉迷于做这些事清
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}确定不会走得太远
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.76,0:13:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再说这也是打发时间的好方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:14:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以平衡希尔维不在的郁闷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但这种复仇对我来说不值得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我最终在面包店女孩身上找到出口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让我烦脑的不是她喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且她认为我可能会喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.79,0:14:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我为了给自己辩护
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我告诉自己说那是她的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她这样玩火会受惩罚的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的献慇勤成了每天必做的事清
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而她最初害羞也没能拒绝我多久
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很好吃  我可以只吃蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:15:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我送你一块
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.76,0:15:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.76,0:15:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老板不在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她在准备晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你怕什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我还以为你每天这样看着蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.10,0:15:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会很讨厌它们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我刚来这里一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不会留很久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}9月份  我要在老佛爷商场里工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一天都在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.93,0:15:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直到8点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你晚上做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你晚上想跟我一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才18岁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么  你父母不让你出门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.66,0:16:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我刚才吃了个杏桃塔和酵母蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有一个苹果派
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的考试结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}需要帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我打扰到你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你害怕见到我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管怎样  我一个月后就离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我陪你走一段如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}过来这边  我告诉你点事清
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我做错什么事清了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不  我告诉过你  不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我们晚上一起玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明晚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要缠着我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们会熟悉的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我看起来像坏人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们去香榭丽舍大街看电影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你应该经常去看电影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的  星期六
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我们星期六一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和朋友一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}男孩  女孩  他们都很蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管什么原因  那就星期六
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不  星期六不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那改天  你父母不让你出门
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.19,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我希望不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就明天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们先吃晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后去香榭丽舍大街
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.69,0:17:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我8点在咖啡店等你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多姆咖啡店  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要穿成什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用  你现在就很好  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈也许不会喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但你说过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.96,0:18:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的  大多时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就说是跟女孩出门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道  也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想玩点小花招吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小花招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我明天7点半经过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我们没法在面包店谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.27,0:18:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要一份蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你给我两份
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你就是同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样的话我们就8点在咖啡店见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}重复一遍 看你明白没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我给你两份蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就是同意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好吧  我现在走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我先走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的名字是杰克琳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再见  杰克琳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我得到了我想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但事清突然的转折让我措手不及
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个女孩不太好追
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本来可以让我良心好受点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:18:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我到底做了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}另外  我就要离开巴黎了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这之前不会发生什么事清
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有其它的顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第二天  星期五
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我参加了口语考试通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我差点没去成约会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我朋友都不在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一想到晚上一个人度过就很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一份曲奇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.76,0:19:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎么呢  受伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}扭伤休息了三个星期
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我还在想怎么没见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我昨天看到了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过你正在思考问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}过来点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}片刻之间  我改变了主意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你吃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我饿了  不用解释了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想一起吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一会下来  我住二楼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我等了15分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我开始反省我的鲁莽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我应该推后和希尔维的约会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天跟面包店女孩出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管怎样  还是有道德的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}终于找到了希尔维
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而继续和面包店女孩约会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}则是不道德的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个意味着真实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}另一个则是错误
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我当时这样对自己说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:21:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事情变得更加复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天开始下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.29,0:21:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而这样正好拯救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.49,0:21:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正好8点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不能走路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.62,0:21:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我找辆的士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下雨的时候不好找
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可以走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}街上没有行人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}面包店女孩如果走出门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就可以看见我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.43,0:21:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我很懦弱地认为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她太远了  没法上来质问我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.02,0:21:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不敢回头看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.35,0:21:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而眼前的路似乎没有尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她看见我们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是她已经在咖啡店等我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.26,0:21:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.16,0:22:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而希尔维这么爽快地答应了约会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我马上知道了原因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我试着给自己找乐子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.96,0:22:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我受不了有人在我门口走来走去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.16,0:22:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也许你不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我的窗户正好面向街道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.09,0:22:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我什么都看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.99,0:22:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我开始发抖  但她还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.79,0:22:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.79,0:22:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你差点让我觉得内疚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是  我当时不能大声叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.29,0:22:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毕竟你有权利选择
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用那些糟糕的蛋糕填饱肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它们很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.30,0:22:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道  我吃过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反正  我知道了你所有的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.43,0:22:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.16,0:22:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}主厨的特别蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们6个月后结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.43,0:22:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后在勒波特大街上住了一段时间

